name: Uber
title: Uber
description: An API to call an Uber car to your location.

endpoints.name: Estimated price range
endpoints.description: The Price Estimates endpoint returns an estimated price range for each product offered at a given location. The price estimate is provided as a formatted string with the full price range and the localized currency symbol.

endpoints.name: User lifetime activity
endpoints.description: The User Activity endpoint returns data about a user's lifetime activity with Uber. The response will include pickup locations and times, dropoff locations and times, the distance of past requests, and information about which products were requested.

endpoints.name: User information
endpoints.description: The User Profile endpoint returns information about the Uber user that has authorized with the application.
